#. <section class="sutta" id="an5.101"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an5.101:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 5"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.101:0.2"
msgid "11. Phāsuvihāravagga"
msgstr "11. Living Comfortably"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: sekhavesārajjasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an5.101:0.3"
msgid "101. Sārajjasutta"
msgstr "101. Assurance"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an5.101:1.1"
msgid "“Pañcime, bhikkhave, sekhavesārajjakaraṇā dhammā."
msgstr "“Mendicants, these five qualities make a trainee assured."

msgctxt "an5.101:1.2"
msgid "Katame pañca?"
msgstr "What five?"

msgctxt "an5.101:1.3"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu saddho hoti, sīlavā hoti, bahussuto hoti, "
"āraddhavīriyo hoti, paññavā hoti."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant is faithful, ethical, learned, energetic, and wise."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an5.101:2.1"
msgid ""
"Yaṃ, bhikkhave, assaddhassa sārajjaṃ hoti, saddhassa taṃ sārajjaṃ na hoti."
msgstr ""
"A person of faith doesn’t have the insecurities of someone who lacks faith."

msgctxt "an5.101:2.2"
msgid "Tasmāyaṃ dhammo sekhavesārajjakaraṇo."
msgstr "So this quality makes a trainee assured."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an5.101:3.1"
msgid ""
"Yaṃ, bhikkhave, dussīlassa sārajjaṃ hoti, sīlavato taṃ sārajjaṃ na hoti."
msgstr ""
"An ethical person doesn’t have the insecurities of someone who is unethical."

msgctxt "an5.101:3.2"
msgid "Tasmāyaṃ dhammo sekhavesārajjakaraṇo."
msgstr "So this quality makes a trainee assured."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an5.101:4.1"
msgid ""
"Yaṃ, bhikkhave, appassutassa sārajjaṃ hoti, bahussutassa taṃ sārajjaṃ na "
"hoti."
msgstr ""
"A learned person doesn’t have the insecurities of a person of little "
"learning."

msgctxt "an5.101:4.2"
msgid "Tasmāyaṃ dhammo sekhavesārajjakaraṇo."
msgstr "So this quality makes a trainee assured."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an5.101:5.1"
msgid ""
"Yaṃ, bhikkhave, kusītassa sārajjaṃ hoti, āraddhavīriyassa taṃ sārajjaṃ na "
"hoti."
msgstr "An energetic person doesn’t have the insecurities of a lazy person."

msgctxt "an5.101:5.2"
msgid "Tasmāyaṃ dhammo sekhavesārajjakaraṇo."
msgstr "So this quality makes a trainee assured."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "an5.101:6.1"
msgid ""
"Yaṃ, bhikkhave, duppaññassa sārajjaṃ hoti, paññavato taṃ sārajjaṃ na hoti."
msgstr "A wise person doesn’t have the insecurities of someone who is witless."

msgctxt "an5.101:6.2"
msgid "Tasmāyaṃ dhammo sekhavesārajjakaraṇo."
msgstr "So this quality makes a trainee assured."

msgctxt "an5.101:6.3"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, pañca sekhavesārajjakaraṇā dhammā”ti."
msgstr "These are the five qualities that make a trainee assured.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.101:6.4"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
